{"tid":296082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方呼籲市民提供馬X珍失蹤消息","createTime":"2017-06-24T09:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T12:42:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6126aa912c4e18d9f187e68fde6b890e0eb46f","tid":296082,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170624/large/1498295909_51a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170624%2Flarge%2F1498295909_51a4.jpg&h=c673cc32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n73歲的馬愛珍，於昨日上午離開其位於屯門寶田邨的住所後便告失蹤，其家人同日向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n馬愛珍身高約1.6米，體重約45公斤，瘦身材，方面型，黃皮膚，蓄短直黑髮。她最後露面時身穿黑色上衣、黑色長褲及黑色鞋，並攜有一個深灰色袋。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲，任何人如有馬愛珍的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 3128或6273 5787或電郵至rmpu-ntn-1@police.gov.hk與新界北總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。"},{"pid":"00ffc3d8c72adb94072993c86a16b93ead7f6cd2","tid":296082,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170624&amp;guid=56871206&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170624%26guid%3D56871206%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=%2F5HrELpN8b2ukEhF%2BEI8ak%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=98d53225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170624%26guid%3D56871206%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=c45592a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170624&amp;guid=56871206&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"3b8580bdbf8365e1ea4401f22407fc915e5c0ee0","tid":296082,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{